text:
Like any other fair price.. budget and beat prices.

Located on ground level hence much easy access for wheel chairs.

Surrounded by Rivervale Plaza, LRT and food courts.

My coupon needs a minimum spending of 40 dollars to be used, and the cashier (loh mui ngoh) did not tell us that we still owed 40 cents to meet my minimum spending. She directly asked us to cancel our coupon. What?
